# PCB — SlimPad

Designed in KiCad 9. 2-layer board, 100×100mm.

## Files
- `slimpad3.kicad_pcb` — PCB layout
- `slimpad1.kicad_sch` — schematic
- `slimpad1.kicad_pro` — project file

## Screenshots
![PCB layout](pcb.jpg)
![Schematic](sch.jpg)

## Specs
| Parameter | Value |
|-----------|-------|
| Board size | 100 × 100 mm |
| Layers | 2 (F.Cu signal, B.Cu GND plane) |
| Thickness | 1.6 mm |
| Switch count | 12 (3×4 matrix) |
| Switch pitch | 19 mm (MX standard) |
| Diode orientation | COL2ROW |

## Components
| Reference | Value | Footprint |
|-----------|-------|-----------|
| SW1–SW12 | MX switch | SW_Cherry_MX_1.00u_PCB |
| D1–D12 | 1N4148 | D_DO-35_SOD27_P7.62mm_Horizontal |
| SW13 | EC11 encoder | RotaryEncoder_Alps_EC11E_Vertical_H20mm |
| U1 | XIAO RP2040 | XIAO-Generic-Hybrid-14P-2.54-21X17.8MM |
| J1 | OLED 4-pin | PinHeader_1x04_P2.54mm_Vertical |

## Pin Mapping
| XIAO Pin | GPIO | Function |
|----------|------|----------|
| D0 | GPIO26 | ROW0 |
| D1 | GPIO27 | ROW1 |
| D2 | GPIO28 | ROW2 |
| D3 | GPIO29 | ROW3 |
| D6 | GPIO0 | COL0 |
| D7 | GPIO1 | COL1 |
| D8 | GPIO2 | COL2 |
| D9 | GPIO4 | ENC A |
| D10 | GPIO3 | ENC B |
| MISO | GPIO16 | OLED SDA |
| TX | GPIO20 | OLED SCL |

## Ordering (JLCPCB)
1. Go to https://jlcpcb.com
2. Upload Gerber ZIP
3. Settings: 2 layers, 1.6mm, FR4, any color
4. Qty: 5 pcs (~$5)
